  "detailed_description": "<h1>The first Episode -“CaseCracker”</h1><p>“CaseCracker 2” is the sequel story of the first episode, between which there lie some connection and relationship. You will get a much better experience with the sequel story by playing the “CaseCrack” first. And surely, if you directly start to play the “CaseCrack 2”, it will not affect the core experience of the game.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>“CaseCrack 2” .the sequel story of “CaseCracker”, is also a text-based detective puzzle game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/f505f580fcf34e25feee4980d6e7b78a.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>As the invited tester, you need to check all the existing clues and information in each case , search for key words and continuously find out more clues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/b2c36a2fc24ca9a43426a778611add4c.poster.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/b2c36a2fc24ca9a43426a778611add4c.webm?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/b2c36a2fc24ca9a43426a778611add4c.mp4?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>While sorting out the fragmented information, you need to reason out and finish tasks such as “monitor surveillance”, “search warrant”, “system access” and “decryption”.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/695eea21ae2b4d9c90d333b73cd07026.poster.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/695eea21ae2b4d9c90d333b73cd07026.webm?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/695eea21ae2b4d9c90d333b73cd07026.mp4?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After collecting all the information , you need to reason out the treads and plots of the whole case, and answer the question of the system to solve the case, after the solution, you can review the records from the “Criminal statement”. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/187219c635cbece0fba195f9b2ab9850.poster.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/187219c635cbece0fba195f9b2ab9850.webm?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/187219c635cbece0fba195f9b2ab9850.mp4?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have a more immersive experience of cracking a criminal case like a policeman   under the system rules with the realistic narrative story . <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/b9b4ec20dc24c338ea19f5bd2354981b.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>You will experience a step-by-step progress of cracking the case with the complex and intricate plot and story where there lie some cross-over relationship among different characters and cases.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/0fa205413fa340adee77d56699dcd456.poster.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/0fa205413fa340adee77d56699dcd456.webm?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/0fa205413fa340adee77d56699dcd456.mp4?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/8f7bce9d7939d58cb764d44126211676.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Beside the mainline, there are also some other bizarre branch and invisible line needed to be dig out. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/8ccf71dab96975af9cbceca5e46afa62.poster.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/8ccf71dab96975af9cbceca5e46afa62.webm?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/8ccf71dab96975af9cbceca5e46afa62.mp4?t=1771161246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/3341b8c76277180468a13c7e03ae0687.avif?t=1771161246\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Players need to find out the clues all by themselves, since there is no alternatives provided. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All the cases happen in one world, independently yet related with each other</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The invisible clue line can be explored beyond the game story, </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Please take it seriously for each choice you make in the one-round word game!</li></ul>",
